original_title: Babad Tanah Leluhur I (Rahasia Bukit Tengkorak)
overview: Jerangkong Hidup (Budi Schwarzkrone) is making trouble in the Karang Sedana kingdom again. Sanata Dharma (Wisnu Wardhana), who is asked to solve this problem, initially refuses because he has entered a retreat and shut himself off from worldly things. However, when the situation continues to deteriorate, Sanata Dharma comes to the rescue and Jerangkong Hidup can be overcome.
title: Babad Tanah Leluhur I (Rahasia Bukit Tengkorak)
